From b9b8eea329f2130c2a99707f38aa4268ceaa4971 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Work Leaf Bench <bench@example.com>
Date: Wed, 10 Jun 2026 20:45:03 +0200
Subject: [PATCH 1/3] ADD pane-focused terminal controls for agent chat
 navigation

Implement Vim-style pane focus, visual selection, agent row introspection, split/window chat actions, and harness coverage so terminal users can inspect and move between Work Leaf command and agent conversations without leaving the TUI.
